Import this project to IntelliJ IDEA CE
You also need gradle and GIT to be installed
After project importing, navigate in Intellij to src->main->java->helpers
open TestBase and try to download/add the missing packages/modules.
For example "import org.slf4j.Logger" -> click on it and add to project
Check and add missing packages also in src->main->test->java->TestClass1 
Then right-click on project root [gradle-selenium-test] -> Run 'Tests in 'gradle-sel...'
Observe
